{"tid":762037,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好再笑小喬bb喇！！","createTime":"2018-07-31T02:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T02:31:07.000Z","uid":191338,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1ff70755294403f2395e2a4d72c4af38c763dcb9","tid":762037,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T02:30:42.000Z","msg":"亞歷克斯和家人見到面具後，均對面具的像真度感到驚訝，片段中亞歷克斯似乎不敢正眼望它，他坦言：「我之前沒想過，這會可能做得到。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/102641_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F102641_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a1d0baa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/102532_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F102532_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5ae38400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/102529_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F102529_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=35eb2b40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/102527_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F102527_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0571de49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/102525_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F102525_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0e2ff94a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/102523_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F102523_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=13cd904f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想買一款小喬bb矽膠面具"},{"pid":"73ae872b7693873e400de899d5f1397abbdc39eb","tid":762037,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T02:31:07.000Z","msg":"【人頭面具】睇唔出喎！跟足敏感患者外貌整面具 方便出街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國25歲男子亞歷克斯患有罕見遺傳病－著色性乾皮症（Xeroderma pigmentosum），對陽光中的紫外線敏感，自3個月大之後，就未試過在日光下活動。BBC電視節目「The Big Life Fix」的發明家，就為亞歷克斯研製出一個超像真矽膠面具，期望協助他活得更自由。<br />\n<br />\n自小患有著色性乾皮症的亞歷克斯，皮膚比常人對紫外線敏感1萬倍，皮膚細胞被陽光中的紫外線破壞之後，不能自行修復，亦極度容易會在年輕時誘發出癌症。亞歷克斯在數個月大時，就曾因為曝露於陽光下而敏感發作，臉孔出現大量水泡。<br />\n<br />\n確診後，亞歷克斯只能夠「晚出早歸」，或戴著一頂特製的、附有面罩的帽，待紫外線指數低於1度時才能外出，生活充滿限制，他慨歎：「我也很想我可以像其他人一樣。」<br />\n<br />\nBBC電視節目「The Big Life Fix」的發明家勞克林（Zoe Laughlin），就運用創意和科技，按亞歷克斯的容貌製造出一個超像真矽膠面具。勞克林先利用特殊攝影機，為亞歷克斯的臉孔拍攝過千張照片，以其樣貌特製3D模具，打造一具能完全抵擋紫外線的矽膠面具。"}]}